Hey Y’ll! Check out my new skiff! ⚓️

node.text:
Back to back casts produced back to back fish 🔥🎣 Artificial only! No live bait needed 💁🏼‍♀️ Had an absolute slay day, full video just went live on YouTube! ⏩ Check it out & lmk what y’all think 🙌🏼 Link in bio!
#artificial #inshore #bikini #fishing #ladyangler #igtv
